  <data name="Text_Seizoen" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>The UEFA Champions League 2025/26 is the 71st edition of the most important tournament in European men's club football, organized by UEFA, and the 34th since the name change. The final is scheduled for May 30, 2026 at the Puskás Aréna in Budapest. The winner qualifies for the UEFA Champions League 2026/27, the UEFA Super Cup 2026, the FIFA Intercontinental Cup 2026 and the Club World Cup 2029. Paris Saint-Germain is the defending champion.</value>
